          "status": "identified",
          "body": "Trello is experiencing slowdowns and failures affecting comment operations, including creating and deleting comments. Users may also experience delays when loading activity views on cards, viewing attachments, using Power-Ups, exporting boards and 'Updates' on home page. \n\nOur team is actively working on the resolution and will likely take up to 7 hours to restore the services back to full functionality. We will provide further update at this time, or earlier if we have additional information to share prior to this resolution.",
